FBIS3-41374 "jptdd008__l94082" JPRS-TDD-94-008-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 23 February 1994 AFRICA SOUTH AFRICA Detectives Seize 91,500 Mandrax Tablets, Arrest 3 Outside Cape Town MB1702113894 Johannesburg SAPA in English 0853 GMT 17 Feb 94 MB1702113894 Johannesburg SAPA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Cape Town Feb 17 SAPA -- Narcotics detectives seized 91,500 mandrax tablets with a street value of about R[rand]1.3 million and arrested two women and a man in Nyanga, outside Cape Town, on Wednesday afternoon. Police said on Thursday 1,500 tablets were found in a house in the area and two women were arrested. Detectives found a further 90,000 mandrax tablets hidden in a minibus parked outside the house and arrested a 42-year-old man. [passage omitted]
